{"tid":2340600,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人若變版Last Christmas","createTime":"2020-12-25T15:23:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T18:16:06.000Z","uid":307910,"like":5,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9073fdef120bb3c1c270c352721ca0d3e11ae37b","tid":2340600,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T15:23:08.000Z","msg":"Last Christmas I gave you my heart<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, and the very next day Kelly gave it away<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nThis year, 人若變好鬼想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到今日仲好掛住kelly<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLast Christmas I gave you my heart<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBut the very next day Kelly gave it away<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (kelly唔要我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\nThis year, 仲係好掛住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nI 會掛住someone special (you again<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\nOnce bitten and twice shy<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋保持距離, 但我仲好掛住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話比我知, 你仲記唔記得我哋嘅感情<br />\nWell, 已經過咗一年，你唔記得我好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Merry Christmas&quot; I wrapped it up and sent it<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nWith a note saying &quot;I love you&quot;, I meant it<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nNow I know what a fool I've been<br />\nBut if you kissed me now, I will let you fool me again<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n.......<br />\nA crowded room, friends with tired eyes<br />\nI'm hiding from you and your soul of ice<br />\nMy God, I thought you were someone to rely on<br />\nMe? I guess I was a shoulder to cry on<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nA face of a lover with a fire in his heart<br />\nA man under cover but you tore me apart<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nOoh-hoo<br />\n（改唔到，太精警<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\nNow you've found a real love, you'll never fool me again<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過呢個回憶係人生上面最好嘅一次 就算過咗去都依然對我好重要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人若變記憶便迷人 情令眼淺了便情深<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c97058deee541d83593b5fbc38cff997778f1b9","tid":2340600,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T15:28:34.000Z","msg":"齋負評唔留言係咩2c<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5c38e6f56d5be73e81248500037e4828124be0","tid":2340600,"uid":329698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:20:27.000Z","msg":"me：未試過Christmas係o緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a5b330acce68a3da56c956fa086d427c549488","tid":2340600,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:27:19.000Z","msg":"連字(音)數都唔啱 都唔知點覆你好"},{"pid":"9d4a17df2383422947ea94ffbb28f2d988381dcd","tid":2340600,"uid":366192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:31:57.000Z","msg":"多才多藝<br />\nkelly識著你真丟架<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369